vgp-edit(1)

# NAME

vgp-edit - HUD symbology text editor

# SYNOPSIS

*vgp-edit* [_file_]

# DESCRIPTION

Minimal vector-rendered text editor. Line numbers appear in an altitude-tape
gutter; the cursor is a crosshair; syntax highlighting uses the HUD
white/yellow/red phosphor palette.

# OPTIONS

Opens _file_ if given, otherwise starts empty.

# KEYBINDINGS

*Arrow keys*
	Move the cursor.

*Ctrl+S*
	Save the current file.

*Escape*
	Close the editor.

# SEE ALSO

*vgp*(1)
